com.akvelon.server.dao.impl

Class SuperStringDao<V extends Entity<java.lang.String>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.akvelon.server.dao.impl.SuperStringDao<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - type of domain object.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Dao<java.lang.String,V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CultureDaoImpl, UnitMeasureDaoImpl

    @Repository
public abstract class SuperStringDao<V extends Entity<java.lang.String>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Dao<java.lang.String,V>
    Implementation of the DAO interface. The class implements all CRUD operations for domain objects whose ID type is String. Child classes must implement three abstract methods from this class.
